channel.title: Looks for experienced server Makers. Co-Admin spot reward!
channel.description: Hi, I can't figure out how to make a server with all the things I want in it. Too complicated for me. So, I decided to have somebody else do it, for a Co-Admin spot on my server. I have an AIM and a YAHOO account to give you the ideas I want for my server. Or we can talk here on the forums. Either way. I'm giving everybody who has some pretty good skills when it comes to making private servers. [br][size=1]Posted on: January 01, 2007, 12:53:30 PM[/size][hr]By the way, sorry I meant to say Co-Owner spot. Not C0-Admin.
